txt.en: 'It is good to see you as well, but this is not a joyous time. I look around and see only death.'
'I persuaded you to take to the dunes Herion. Now I ask for you to return to Linhir.'
'I shall not bicker any longer with thee. Come let us pay our respects.'
'Do you care about Garvir and Aragorn's orders to protect Linhir?'
'Brother it is good to see you again. We have accomplished much for Gondor in our time apart.'
'If you do not apologise to Garvir, I will in your stead.'
'I see noble men who sacrificed themselves for our land!'
'Quiet now. Let us all pay our respects to these poor souls.'
'[placeholder] defeated the leader of the enemy. Victory is at hand, brother!'
'Erchar, I too care about these men.'
